Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.02,0:01:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是有关你还是这个森林的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.70,0:02:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都作为我一个人的秘密藏在心里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…为什么不对我说更多的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不能再多见你几次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.12,0:02:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在困难的时候帮助我们 你究竟从哪里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.12,0:02:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.68,0:02:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.14,0:02:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…我想和你做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…这我无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 就想你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.99,0:02:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.58,0:02:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(440,0){\fn方正粗圆_GBK}{\fs45}{\pos(320,450)}{\b0}{\1c&HD7FFFF&}{\4c&HFFC1C1&}{\shad1}{\bord0}心有灵犀！小小兔与天马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好！那个天马在这个世界上根本没个影儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 要捉着它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有找到作为它宿主的那个拥有美丽梦想的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记那个天马可是握有能征服整个世界的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉鲁科尼亚大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那个美梦宿主发现了天马拥有的力量会怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个人发现一匹有着能征服世界能力的天马
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就住在自己的美梦中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就能利用天马为所欲为了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有美丽梦想的人会想着征服世界吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她开始这么想的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论多么美丽的梦想 也会变得扭曲不堪哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰眼说得有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这点 天马自己比任何人都要清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.17,0:03:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马是不会对自己的宿主说任何有关自己力量的话题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她发现的时候那就是天马开始寻找新的宿主之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.92,0:04:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝮蛇火花子～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 虎眼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的谈话 你听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是说 天马就是“影”是么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有着能通过某人的影子潜入这人内心的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马是“影”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过潜入它的影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就算意味着以此可以找到它的宿主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就能马上明白天马的宿主是谁了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎眼大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的能力是迷惑人心 并偷走它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能偷到天马宿主的心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天马就是我们的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以下次的任务 我会把你带上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔画完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.23,0:05:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～小小兔好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿～是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小兔 看上去就像个名画家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯哼～请叫我艺术家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一般般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的画呢？九助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！不让看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.43,0:05:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更科同学 桃原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们已经画完了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点点 森野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月野同学你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月野同学 你那是什么打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在模仿前阵子在电视上看到的名画家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行 月野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你认真对待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家觉得打扮成这样能画得更好一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的画 画得怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯 画得很生动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色彩也用得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.32,0:06:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样的画我可没办法打高分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主题是风景画对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是有什么就画什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那里没有的东西画了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能叫做写生了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我觉得它和景色很配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可真是固执啊 森野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到现在还是单身哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 现在还有时间 你最好重新改过再交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家都认真画了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到森野老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很冷漠 很难接近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是她讨厌小孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难相处啊 那些孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.45,0:07:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的目标就是她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不怎么样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就年龄来看的话 该是你的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.39,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有心跳的感觉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死鱼！你偶尔也干点活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要！首先我对女人没兴趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是噢是噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.37,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你 是不是要我这样的大哥才对你胃口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么人家要对你这种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头脑简单 只有肌肉 四肢发达！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是～就是这样 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在考虑让他们把天马引出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在抓到了天马 所有的功劳都是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单！单！双！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.00,0:08:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！动作快点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么飞机！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是第三根电线杆吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是给我赶快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始咯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀石头布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.90,0:08:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔你输了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.19,0:08:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再走三根电线杆的距离哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么又是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！你给我等一下小小兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.44,0:08:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道她就不会想想至少分担一半吗！真是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说 擅长猜拳才说明那家伙性格恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！东西！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苹果！肉！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～～鸡蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你好 月野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这人是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教美术的森野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好！初次见面！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！我家小小兔麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？我家小小兔在学校的表现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别作出一副家长模样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.63,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定是一副臭屁样 给您添了很多麻烦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你别一副家长模样！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月野同学在班级里很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是谁都能很容易成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有点羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊对了！鸡蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系 请不用放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就回头见 月野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 你在学校表现不错？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:09:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我也不是和每个人都能成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当老师…就算到了周日也还是一个老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留步 那边的小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是工作的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在烦恼着什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸上愁云密布哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把烦恼的女性从困惑中解救出来 就是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是特别服务 免费为您提供人生咨询
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然愁容看上去也很迷人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.02,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想笑容一定更适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让自己变得更美丽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当作是自己被骗了 跟我说说看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从小时候起 就想要成为一个老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦成了教师 却完全无法和孩子们好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:11:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样是否还能继续作为教师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都开始考虑这样的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是想着这是把天马和水手战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引出来的计划！我还真不想干了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要忍耐 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要做一个让孩子喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…可现在的你已经无需有任何担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快你就能告别这痛苦的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我、告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不会让你走哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…讨厌！我累了！好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.74,0:11:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要搭顺风车吗？两位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是我的王子殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我参观参观吧 你那美丽的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.17,0:12:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦！这真是！多美丽的梦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…梦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:13:00.05,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月亮危机 变身
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.37,0:13:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没中…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:36.29,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}给我住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:42.00,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}年复一年向自己深爱着的学生伸出援手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:43.73,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}老师是大家的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:45.45,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}敢打老师的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:46.94,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}爱与正义的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:49.36,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}水手服美少女战士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.97,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}水手月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.15,0:13:58.18,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}水手小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.98,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}我们要代替月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.73,0:14:02.74,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}惩罚你！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正等着你们呢 水手战士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.07,0:14:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个总是攻击女性傲慢无礼的恶棍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在！水手小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.43,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}拜托了 天马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.65,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}请守护大家的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.46,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&FF77FF&}闪烁呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 我的放射线妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走壁小丑蝮蛇火花子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是蝮蛇火花子～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.37,0:14:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就交给你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了！小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…是你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是天马的宿主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多漂亮的马啊～真好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要对天马做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都不会做哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是你的马哟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 这里是你的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里看到的所有都是你的东西哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来～拿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊拉～怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧～拿上缰绳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样 天马就是你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的孩子呢～你难道不想要这匹天马么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道 这可不是一匹普通的马哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这匹马的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是世界也能成为自己的东西哟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来～快拿上它吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想是要和所有喜欢我的人成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想要天马！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和它做朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.36,0:17:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是以力量迫使它听我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.03,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说没有任何意义！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.99,0:17:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻啊你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想要和它做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全地支配它不是更有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那由我来决定！不是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是赶快滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.83,0:17:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在！水手月亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:05.94,SP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFF66FF&}月光华丽冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退出舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小月亮…发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.28,0:18:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把车开过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！那片云！好像奶油泡芙！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢！那就把它画得美味一点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！画画真有趣！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真开心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！最喜欢你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了！那个奇怪的人已经被水手月亮赶跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么…水手月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话 送您一程
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我还能走…谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回头见 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月野同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.46,0:19:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次写生课上的画…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你还是交了画着天马的画呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还是觉得那样才是好看的画呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且呐 当我看着那个风景的时候就觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有天马在那里非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常珍视那份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.48,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管画得多好 我都不会给你好分数的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！但我还是喜欢这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真是个不可思议的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也真的很喜欢那幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 小小兔 回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“喜欢这样的自己”…吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好！我可不会认输！ 小鬼头们！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…想要和你成为朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要留在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:20:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后就能一直见到你了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就像这样只有两人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那！今晚就能和你聊天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！对了！稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…没…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我们虽然一直叫你天马…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你真正的名字吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.87,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正的名字叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…这个我现在还不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.09,0:21:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以后可以慢慢相处…对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:08.48,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(310,478)\fs29\fsp1}自从与你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.48,0:22:13.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}心中的深处闪烁着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:19.80,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}无法舍弃对你的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:24.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}只能静静的闭上双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.14,0:22:28.89,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}过去的些许小事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.89,0:22:34.57,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}极为平常的言语也好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.15,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}当想起之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.15,0:22:44.32,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}泪水就不知不觉的流出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.10,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(168,472)\fs29\fsp1}现在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.10,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(250,480)\fs40\fsp1}Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.10,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(352,480)\fs40\fsp1}Baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:48.10,EDEN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(451,478)\fs41\fsp1.5}love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.10,0:22:53.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}这样哭泣的夜晚也总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:59.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(309,478)\fs29\fsp1}怀念往昔 笑着相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:05.64,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(317,478)\fs29\fsp2}成为相爱的恋人吧......
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原谅！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.60,0:23:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫竟然要住在小丽家！？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这没什么好大惊小怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个人！以前交往过啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.55,0:23:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一度消散的热情再次被点燃的话要怎么办！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小卫！不要…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.57,0:23:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级水手月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护小卫！忍者小兔的醋意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.97,0:23:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光传递着爱的讯息


